{"tid":2058454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台顧問委員會首次開會 主席向港台提出要製作有關國安法節目","createTime":"2020-06-10T07:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T08:00:52.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e86d1dce623be00b1b55d1c3571f3f596ddd72e8","tid":2058454,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"【港台製作節目講解國安法】<br />\n<br />\n香港電台顧問委員會工作小組召開首次會議，並於港台管理層會面。港台顧問委員會主席陳建強會後表示，向港台提出製作關於國安法的節目，並要清晰、精準、客觀。他指由港台製作與國安法有關節目跟港台管理層的想法是「不謀而合」。<br />\n<br />\n他指所有委員也認同需要國安法相關節目，並不存在任何施壓。希望港台能夠真真正正做到一個公共廣播機構。<br />\n<br />\n陳表示港台作為公告廣播機構及一個政府部門是責無旁貸，應該正面將國安法的背景、因由和細節向市民解釋清楚。陳建強認為市民現在接受很多假新聞和假想法，希望這些節目能讓市民「唔好再有任何誤會」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳指出廣播處長向他保證會確守《港台約章》及「一個中國」原則。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1181276915549049/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F1181276915549049%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVawzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=c5ac9d5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1181276915549049/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"f77dc46feacd11a05db35c38eefa9b683006aa90","tid":2058454,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a00807d8f280edd33cd45d26ddd2df08598d891","tid":2058454,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"仲要只能由正面方向"},{"pid":"bb8d3775df80c7cb48a76fdf62453c81e51b0f42","tid":2058454,"uid":18477,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:41:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他指所有委員也認同需要國安法相關節目，並不存在任何施壓。</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n喂所有你口中叫做委員嘅嘢全部都係red objects嚟㗎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab2b0a1903d96dc2365287391aad7cbd81224b2","tid":2058454,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:43:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e795195cc5e28b77d5703d424afe652947f2d255","tid":2058454,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"建議全面採用加速主義<br />\n成個節目都係不斷重覆五個紅色大字<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國安大法好</span></span><br />\n播足半個鐘is ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d64ccfeeddded0ead6cffb55ef6208ddf8e4e7","tid":2058454,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"國安法節目<br />\n講下劉曉波李旺陽都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3b0a9d280f38c9b6dad690f4403368316e134c","tid":2058454,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03d64ccfeeddded0ead6cffb55ef6208ddf8e4e7","tid":2058454,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"國安法節目<br />\n講下劉曉波李旺陽都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"劉曉波抵死<br />\n你旺陽抵死"},{"pid":"f27282f7669cde749af932ed7dd83d37b9edfa95","tid":2058454,"uid":113498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"通訊局話要持平，咁要講埋銅鑼灣書店、上訪者、維權律師個啲先得喎"},{"pid":"76c71fc19f441856d88e63a8c246cdad0c6ad585","tid":2058454,"uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa3b0a9d280f38c9b6dad690f4403368316e134c","tid":2058454,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03d64ccfeeddded0ead6cffb55ef6208ddf8e4e7","tid":2058454,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,